              "raw": " {\n    \"brand\": \"Osprey\",\n    \"title\": \"Atmos AG 65 Backcountry Trekking Backpack\",\n    \"price\": 340.00,\n    \"description\": \"The Osprey Atmos AG 65 features the award-winning Anti-Gravity suspension system, offering unmatched ventilation and load-carrying comfort for multi-day backcountry trekking. The continuous lightweight mesh backpanel wraps seamlessly from the upper back down through the hipbelt, distributing heavy loads evenly while maximizing airflow. Highly adjustable Fit-on-the-Fly shoulder harnesses and hipbelt straps allow hikers to achieve a perfect, customized anatomical fit. Constructed from high-tenacity recycled nylon with a PFC-free DWR coating, it withstands severe trail abrasion. Multiple access points, integrated raincovers, and dedicated trekking pole attachments make this premium pack a global trekking favorite.\",\n    \"stock\": 4,\n    \"imageURL\": \"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1553062407-98eeb64c6a62\",\n    \"categoryId\": \"71416b52-480c-4aa8-9cea-05f437a3d2b1\"\n  }",
